Honami: (I have to make it so everyone can understand how they feel too...!)
Kohane & Emu: ——! ————♪
Honami: (We're finally in sync... This is absolutely incredible...!!)
Honami: (We did it. This is it...!)
Honami: Everyone, that was amazing!
